{"type":"tool_result","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:07:12.275Z","tool_id":"run_shell_command_1777684032116_0","status":"success","output":"commit 6901ffc90f8ca18006ae30574f536a02efe973ea\nAuthor: Anthony Ainsworth <anthony@cascadiantech.com>\nDate:   Fri May 1 17:31:49 2026 -0700\n\n    feat(narrative-api): add events tail endpoint [T-002@20260502T001347Z]\n    \n    GET /events?since_event_id=…&domain=… wraps the deploy-side narrative\n    event store with the same lazy-import / mock-injection pattern used by\n    /memory/search. Tailing from a checkpoint excludes the checkpoint itself\n    and returns only newer events; domain filter accepts either a single\n    value or repeated query params. Defends against stores that ignore the\n    checkpoint by re-filtering server-side.\n    \n    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n src/cypherclaw/narrative_api/__init__.py |  10 +-\n src/cypherclaw/narrative_api/app.py      |  73 ++++++++++-\n src/cypherclaw/narrative_api/events.py   | 214 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++\n src/cypherclaw/narrative_api/schemas.py  |  21 +++\n tests/test_narrative_api_events.py       | 201 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++\n 5 files changed, 514 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)"}
